Genetically Engineered Crop Production

Graphs of GE crop production using ISAAA data

Genetically Engineered Crop Production

Derek Michael Wright

2020-01-01

library(agData) # devtools::install_github("derekmichaelwright/agData")
# Prep data
xx <- agData_ISAAA_Area %>% mutate(Hectares = Hectares / 1000000)
# Plot
mp <- ggplot(xx, aes(x = Year, y = Hectares)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", alpha = 0.5) +
  geom_line(color = "darkred", size = 2) +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(1996,2000,2005,2010,2015),
                     minor_breaks = seq(1996, 2020, by = 1)) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(min(xx$Year)+0.5, max(xx$Year)-0.5)) +
  theme_agData() +
  labs(title = "Global Area of Genetically Engineered Crops", 
       y = "Million Hectares", x = NULL,
       caption = "\xa9 www.dblogr.com/  |  Data: www.isaaa.org/")
ggsave("GE_Crops_ISAAA_01.png", mp, width = 6, height = 4)

# Prep data
xx <- agData_ISAAA_Area %>% 
  mutate(Hectares = Hectares / 1000000,
         Percent.Change = ifelse(Year %in% c(1997, 1998, 1999), NA, Percent.Change),
         plus_minus = plus_minus / 1000000) %>%
  gather(Trait, Value, 2:ncol(.))
# Plot
mp <- ggplot(xx, aes(x = Year, y = Value)) + 
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", alpha = 0.7, color = "Black", fill = "darkred") + 
  facet_grid(Trait~., scales = "free_y") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(1996,2000,2005,2010,2015),
                     minor_breaks = seq(1996, 2020, by = 1)) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(min(xx$Year)+0.4, max(xx$Year)-0.4)) +
  theme_agData() +
  labs(title = "Global Area of Genetically Engineered Crops", 
       y = "Million Hectares", x = NULL,
       caption = "\xa9 www.dblogr.com/  |  Data: www.isaaa.org/")
ggsave("GE_Crops_ISAAA_02.png", mp, width = 6, height = 4)

# Prep data
xx <- agData_ISAAA_DVDDVG
# Plot
mp <- ggplot(xx, aes(x = Year, y = Hectares / 1000000, color = Area)) + 
  geom_line(size = 2) + 
  scale_color_manual(values = c("darkgreen","darkred")) +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(1996,2000,2005,2010,2015),
                     minor_breaks = seq(1996, 2020, by = 1)) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(min(xx$Year)+0.5, max(xx$Year)-0.5)) +
  theme_agData(legend.position = "bottom") +
  labs(title = "Global Area of Genetically Engineered Crops", 
       y = "Million Hectares", x = NULL,
       caption = "\xa9 www.dblogr.com/  |  Data: www.isaaa.org//")
ggsave("GE_Crops_ISAAA_03.png", mp, width = 6, height = 4)

mp <- ggplot(xx, aes(x = Year, y = plus_minus, fill = Crop)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  facet_grid(Crop~., scales = "free_y") +
  scale_fill_manual(values = agData_Colors) +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(1996,2000,2005,2010,2015),
                     minor_breaks = seq(1996, 2020, by = 1)) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(min(xx$Year)+0.4, max(xx$Year)-0.4)) +
  theme_agData(legend.position = "none") +
  labs(title = "Change of GE Crop Hectares Year to Year", x = NULL,
       caption = "\xa9 www.dblogr.com/  |  Data: www.isaaa.org/")

# Prep Data
xx <- agData_ISAAA_CropPercent %>% 
  gather(Trait, Value, 3:ncol(.)) %>%
  filter(Crop != "Others", Trait != "Percent.Transgenic") 
# Plot
mp <- ggplot(xx, aes(x = Year, y = Value, color = Trait)) +
  geom_line(size = 2) +
  facet_wrap(Crop~., ncol= 2, scales = "free_y") +
  scale_color_manual(values = agData_Colors) +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(2000,2005,2010,2015),
                     minor_breaks = seq(1996, 2020, by = 1)) +
  theme_agData(legend.position = "bottom") +
  labs(title = "Adoption of Transgenic Crops", y = "Percent", x = NULL,
       caption = "\xa9 www.dblogr.com/  |  Data: www.isaaa.org/")
ggsave("GE_Crops_ISAAA_10.png", mp, width = 6, height = 4)

#Prep Data
xx<- agData_ISAAA_Country
yy <- xx %>% filter(Million.Hectares > 3) %>% pull(Area)
xx <- xx %>% filter(Area %in% unique(yy)) %>%
  arrange(desc(Million.Hectares)) %>%
  mutate(Area = factor(Area, levels = unique(.$Area)))
xE <- xx %>% top_n(1, Year) %>% pull(Million.Hectares) %>% round(1)
# Plot
mp <- ggplot(xx, aes(x = Year, y = Million.Hectares, color = Area)) + 
  geom_line(size = 1.5) + 
  scale_color_manual(values = agData_Colors) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = seq(0,80, by = 10), 
                     sec.axis = sec_axis(~ ., breaks = xE[1:6])) +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = c(1996,2000,2005,2010,2015),
                     minor_breaks = seq(1996, 2020, by = 1)) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(min(xx$Year)+0.5, max(xx$Year)-1)) +
  theme_agData() +
  labs(title = "Area of GE Crop by Country", y = "Million Hectares", x = NULL,
       caption = "\xa9 www.dblogr.com/  |  Data: www.isaaa.org/")
ggsave("GE_Crops_ISAAA_11.png", mp, width = 6, height = 4)

#Prep Data
xx<- agData_ISAAA_Country %>%
  arrange(desc(Million.Hectares)) %>%
  mutate(Area = factor(Area, levels = unique(.$Area)))
# Plot
ggplot(xx, aes(x = Year, y = Million.Hectares)) + 
  geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
  facet_wrap(Area~., scales = "free_y", ncol = 6) +
  theme_agData() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0.5)) +
  labs(title = "Area of GE Crop by Country", y = "Million Hectares", x = NULL,
       caption = "\xa9 www.dblogr.com/  |  Data: www.isaaa.org/")

ggsave("GE_Crops_ISAAA_12.png", width = 15, height = 15)

xx <- agData_NBT_Limits %>% 
  mutate(Limiting.Factor = as.character(Limiting.Factor),
         PercentLabel = paste(Percent, "%"))
xx$Limiting.Factor[9] <- "Inadequate infrastructure"
xx <- xx %>% mutate(Limiting.Factor = factor(Limiting.Factor, levels = rev(Limiting.Factor)))
mp <- ggplot(xx, aes(x = Limiting.Factor, y = Percent, label = PercentLabel)) + 
  geom_bar(stat = "identity", alpha = 0.8, color = "black", fill = "darkred") + 
  geom_text(color = "white", nudge_y = -1.5) + 
  theme_agData() + 
  coord_flip() +
  labs(title = "Regulatory Barriers for NBTs", x = NULL,
       caption = "\xa9 www.dblogr.com/  |  Data: ?") 
ggsave("GE_Crops_ISAAA_14.png", mp, width = 6, height = 4)
